{"tid":2505691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度海嘯疫情｜「連死也無法死得安詳」 火葬場工人：人被當成牲畜看待","createTime":"2021-04-26T22:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T23:46:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee8707d77bf98a19cd89b8ada231b0955f074f9","tid":2505691,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:26:04.000Z","msg":"「屍體運到就火葬」 火葬場工人：像打扙<br />\n由於患者太多，印度甚至連死者身後事也只能草草處理。印度教徒篤信人死後最好有繁複的儀式，讓靈魂從輪迴中解放，但目前當地太多屍體需要處理，也無法再舉辦太多儀式，火葬場工人坦言：「我們只能在每次有屍體運到就開始火葬，就像我們在打仗似的。」<br />\n<br />\n馬爾霍特拉（Charanjeev Malhotra）在墳場負責火化屍體已數十年，他坦言從未遇過如此嚴峻的境況，形容無法相信自己身在印度首都，「患者無法獲得氧氣，被人當作牲畜看待」，火葬資源亦不足。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210427/O5OG4DQN3FE4RB7ZVYF5B6F23U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210427%2FO5OG4DQN3FE4RB7ZVYF5B6F23U%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=a15fb7be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210427%2FO5OG4DQN3FE4RB7ZVYF5B6F23U%2F&h=5ce3d08b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210427/O5OG4DQN3FE4RB7ZVYF5B6F23U/</a>"},{"pid":"0c3a01ecee4aa5584ac01f09f40758ed0e033fed","tid":2505691,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:28:50.000Z","msg":"同一時間香港，連個爛鬼噴水池都要湧去睇，莫非香港人抵抗力仲勁過印度人？"},{"pid":"21057f8dc1ad674d793b3ba90f4ec0f173f80fed","tid":2505691,"uid":177089,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0c3a01ecee4aa5584ac01f09f40758ed0e033fed","tid":2505691,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:28:50.000Z","msg":"同一時間香港，連個爛鬼噴水池都要湧去睇，莫非香港人抵抗力仲勁過印度人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:38:48.000Z","msg":"第二句同第三句邏輯關係係乜野？"},{"pid":"52169c928b9af1c2a96ee9ae089d3f04ffd15ce8","tid":2505691,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:56:18.000Z","msg":"叫支那賠啦<br />\n每條人命一千萬美元"},{"pid